front.title: •Slave I, Symbol Of Fear
front.gametext: May add 2 pilots and 2 passengers. Power +1 for each opponent's starship here. While Jango or Boba Fett piloting, immune to attrition < 5.
front.lore: Originally designed as a planetary defense craft. Uses restricted jamming technology, allowing it to appear out of nowhere. Contains many hidden armaments.

pulledBy: Short Range Fighters & Watch Your Back!
